2
00:00:19,850 --> 00:00:24,880
song title

3
00:00:24,880 --> 00:00:28,700
 ♫ Heavens strike with thunderous wrath ♫ 

4
00:00:28,700 --> 00:00:32,520
 ♫ Mountains and rivers shatter before my eyes ♫ 

5
00:00:32,520 --> 00:00:35,680
 ♫ Endless splendor
cultivated through lifetimes ♫ 

6
00:00:35,680 --> 00:00:39,490
 ♫ Turns to dust between my fingers
in an instant ♫ 

7
00:00:40,280 --> 00:00:44,180
 ♫ When the line
between good and evil is clear ♫ 

8
00:00:44,180 --> 00:00:48,240
 ♫ Countless souls drift
into the boundless wilds ♫ 

9
00:00:48,240 --> 00:00:51,700
 ♫ Carrying the spirit fire forward ♫ 

10
00:00:51,700 --> 00:00:56,780
♫  I defy fate just to remain by your side  ♫

11
00:00:56,780 --> 00:01:00,840
 ♫ Falling into love's abyss ♫ 

12
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:04,660
 ♫ Like heavy rain pouring down ♫ 

13
00:01:04,660 --> 00:01:08,560
 ♫ Drunk on romance ♫ 

14
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:12,300
 ♫ In a blink, love and hate
vanish into illusion ♫ 

15
00:01:12,300 --> 00:01:16,240
 ♫ Falling into endless love ♫ 

16
00:01:16,240 --> 00:01:19,440
 ♫ Stirring waves upending a lifetime ♫ 

17
00:01:19,440 --> 00:01:22,660
 ♫ Even if this life leads to ruin ♫ 

18
00:01:22,660 --> 00:01:27,020
 ♫ I still choose to be entangled with you ♫ 

19
00:01:27,020 --> 00:01:30,125
 ♫ Through all lifetimes ♫ 

20
00:01:30,125 --> 00:01:36,620
 

21
00:01:36,620 --> 00:01:39,800
 

22
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:41,750
There's no time to dwell on it.

23
00:01:41,750 --> 00:01:46,390
While he's wounded by the array,
we capture him.

24
00:01:46,390 --> 00:01:49,750
Remember this. Leave him alive.

25
00:01:49,750 --> 00:01:51,880
Shi Qian Lv.

26
00:02:04,960 --> 00:02:09,550
Shi Qian Lv, you spent centuries scheming

27
00:02:09,550 --> 00:02:12,040
and went to such lengths
to build Baifeng Mountain,

28
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:14,990
all so you could seize control
of Gengchen Celestial Palace

29
00:02:14,990 --> 00:02:17,850
and no longer be restrained by the Sima clan.

30
00:02:18,710 --> 00:02:21,990
Now, everything is about to fall apart
when you're this close to success.

31
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:26,130
Does that please you?

32
00:02:26,130 --> 00:02:31,810
Sect Master Shi. Was Baifeng Mountain really your doing?

33
00:02:32,990 --> 00:02:36,180
Don't listen to him! He's slandering me!

34
00:02:36,180 --> 00:02:40,990
Sima Jiao, I thought
you still had a shred of conscience, so I defended you at every turn.

35
00:02:40,990 --> 00:02:43,830
But you treat human lives like nothing.

36
00:02:43,830 --> 00:02:47,200
Don't blame us for no longer protecting you!

37
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:50,430
- Everyone, don't be misled by him!
- That's right.

38
00:02:50,430 --> 00:02:54,320
He just wants to drag
Gengchen Celestial Palace down with him.

39
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:57,740
If he manages to kill
the Spirit Fire completely, that will be the real disaster.

40
00:02:57,740 --> 00:03:00,200
You want my life?

41
00:03:00,200 --> 00:03:02,080
Keep dreaming.

42
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:06,930
The likes of you aren't capable
of bringing me down.

43
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:28,230
Shi Qian Lv, so you've really reached
the Grand Ascend realm.

44
00:04:28,230 --> 00:04:31,610
No wonder you've been pushing
your secret plans at Baifeng Mountain.

45
00:04:31,610 --> 00:04:34,100
Let me guess.

46
00:04:34,100 --> 00:04:39,000
You must have hidden
another Spirit Fire somewhere,

47
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:43,480
planning to use my clan's secret to achieve your goal.

48
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:45,080
Another Spirit Fire?

49
00:04:45,080 --> 00:04:48,320
Sima Jiao, stop spouting lies!

50
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:53,280
If I die here with everyone on the mountain and leave you no trace of Fengshan blood,

51
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:56,430
then your grand dream will be over.

52
00:05:12,060 --> 00:05:19,440
 ♫ All beings are but fleeting mayflies,
deceived ♫ 

53
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:22,740
 ♫ Only with both love and hate
can one fight relentlessly ♫ 

54
00:05:22,740 --> 00:05:31,040
 ♫ To forge the boundless Great Way
as its creator ♫ 

55
00:05:32,580 --> 00:05:35,180
 ♫ Rewrite the starry tides of time ♫ 

56
00:05:35,180 --> 00:05:37,570
 ♫ Dye the moon and sky in crimson light ♫ 

57
00:05:37,570 --> 00:05:40,170
He wants to throw his life away and take us down with him!

58
00:05:40,170 --> 00:05:42,450
Stop him together!

59
00:05:43,230 --> 00:05:45,460
It's useless.

60
00:05:45,460 --> 00:05:48,020
 ♫ Transform our parting's elegy ♫ 

61
00:05:48,020 --> 00:05:53,680
 ♫ Strength bows to nature's law alone ♫ 

62
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:56,840
 ♫ So what if we perish? ♫ 

63
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:04,320
Sima Jiao, you...

64
00:06:04,320 --> 00:06:06,860
He really does look like he's at his limit.

65
00:06:06,860 --> 00:06:09,520
His body is about to give out.

66
00:06:11,150 --> 00:06:13,610
Are you afraid?

67
00:06:13,610 --> 00:06:18,660
The ones who should be afraid
are those people over there.

68
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:26,960
Sima Jiao, if it hurts too much, just stop.

69
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:32,240
If you're going to die anyway, there's no point in dragging out your suffering for their sake.

70
00:06:34,660 --> 00:06:37,350
Looks like I'll be dying here today.

71
00:06:37,350 --> 00:06:42,880
But I've already had such a long holiday, so I guess I can't complain.

72
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:46,100
 ♫ To save you, to save me ♫ 

73
00:06:46,100 --> 00:06:52,233
 My destiny is to live a carefree life, eating, drinking, and having fun. 

74
00:06:53,490 --> 00:06:57,930
 Grandmaster. Does this mean I don't have to
be buried with you? 

75
00:06:57,930 --> 00:07:00,020
 You don't want to die? 

76
00:07:00,020 --> 00:07:02,450
 Of course not. 

77
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:06,860
 I have nothing left in this world
worth clinging to. 

78
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:09,910
 But she... She still wants to live. 

79
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:13,670
She still wants to live.

80
00:07:17,230 --> 00:07:18,910
Forget it.

81
00:07:18,910 --> 00:07:20,810
Forget what?

82
00:07:22,660 --> 00:07:27,350
 ♫ For the healing of wounds ♫ 

83
00:07:27,350 --> 00:07:29,440
What is he doing now?

84
00:07:30,340 --> 00:07:34,540
 ♫ To protect the vastness ♫ 

85
00:07:34,540 --> 00:07:38,220
 ♫ For you, for me ♫ 

86
00:07:38,220 --> 00:07:42,380
 ♫ For the light of dawn ♫ 

87
00:07:42,380 --> 00:07:52,140
 ♫ I'll face promises like a moth to a flame ♫ 

88
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:56,590
Grandmaster, let's go.

89
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:02,840
- Come on.
- All right.

90
00:08:05,980 --> 00:08:07,940
Grandmaster?

91
00:08:09,030 --> 00:08:10,560
Go, now.

92
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:12,520
You can't walk anymore?

93
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:17,270
I can't. Run on your own.

94
00:08:17,270 --> 00:08:19,180
Hold on a little longer.

95
00:08:20,230 --> 00:08:21,440
Get up.

96
00:08:21,440 --> 00:08:23,030
Don't you know how to run away?

97
00:08:23,030 --> 00:08:25,660
Come on, Grandmaster.
Just hold on a little longer.

98
00:08:26,790 --> 00:08:28,230
You want to take me with you?

99
00:08:28,230 --> 00:08:29,670
Yes.

100
00:08:30,780 --> 00:08:32,280
Are you trying to die?

101
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:34,320
No.

102
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:36,470
If you drag me along, you'll die for sure.

103
00:08:36,470 --> 00:08:38,440
You're not that foolish, are you?

104
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:40,330
This isn't foolish.

105
00:08:40,330 --> 00:08:42,470
You've saved me so many times.

106
00:08:42,470 --> 00:08:44,230
Pull yourself together.

107
00:08:44,230 --> 00:08:47,980
Tell me where it's safer to run.

108
00:08:47,980 --> 00:08:50,010
Just go.

109
00:08:53,160 --> 00:08:55,080
Grandmaster?

110
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:57,560
S-Sima Jiao!

111
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:59,280
Sima Jiao!

112
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:00,980
Wake up!

113
00:09:00,980 --> 00:09:02,850
Sima Jiao!

114
00:09:04,990 --> 00:09:06,720
 What's on his leg? 

115
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:09,040
Why is it glowing?

116
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:15,204
 

117
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:33,510
Where is this?

118
00:09:34,190 --> 00:09:37,200
Why does it feel like
I've stepped into someone else's domain?

119
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:39,550
Since fate has brought you here,

120
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:43,150
don't be in such a hurry to leave.

121
00:10:06,180 --> 00:10:08,112
 

122
00:10:11,650 --> 00:10:15,460
Young man, it looks like you still remember me.

123
00:10:15,460 --> 00:10:19,820
So... It really is you.

124
00:10:25,410 --> 00:10:29,980
Are you here to kill me or to save me?

125
00:10:29,980 --> 00:10:34,620
Either is possible.

126
00:10:34,620 --> 00:10:38,990
But before that, there is a question that must be answered.

127
00:10:38,990 --> 00:10:42,140
And what if I have no patience to answer you?

128
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:48,490
This is not a question for you to answer.

129
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:15,660
Nian Jiu.

130
00:11:16,350 --> 00:11:17,400
You're awake.

131
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:18,950
Here.

132
00:11:21,350 --> 00:11:22,560
How do you feel?

133
00:11:22,560 --> 00:11:26,340
Ru Ling, why am I here?

134
00:11:26,340 --> 00:11:27,530
Where is the Grandmaster?

135
00:11:27,530 --> 00:11:29,440
How is he now?

136
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:32,710
The Shi family noticed your movements
and attacked you.

137
00:11:32,710 --> 00:11:36,750
I rescued you when no one was watching and secretly brought you back here.

138
00:11:36,750 --> 00:11:38,700
As for the Grandmaster, don't worry.

139
00:11:38,700 --> 00:11:42,810
The Shi family and the other palaces
failed to subdue him.

140
00:11:42,810 --> 00:11:47,320
But he and Ting Yan are currently missing.

141
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:49,780
Missing?

142
00:11:49,780 --> 00:11:51,110
Then I must find him right away.

143
00:11:51,110 --> 00:11:52,320
Wait.

144
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:55,160
If you rush out now,
you'll only make things worse.

145
00:11:55,160 --> 00:11:57,000
Sit down.

146
00:11:59,280 --> 00:12:03,880
The Shi family and the other palaces are searching everywhere for the Grandmaster.

147
00:12:03,880 --> 00:12:06,590
If you go now,
you'll draw attention to yourself,

148
00:12:06,590 --> 00:12:09,630
and you may end up injured again,
just like this time.

149
00:12:09,630 --> 00:12:10,750
But the Grandmaster...

150
00:12:10,750 --> 00:12:11,830
Don't worry.

151
00:12:11,830 --> 00:12:16,950
If he and Ting Yan managed to escape, I'm sure they'll be fine.

152
00:12:18,230 --> 00:12:20,960
Listen, I can move around more freely than you.

153
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:23,440
I'll go out and see how the search went.

154
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:25,630
You stay here and wait for me.

155
00:12:44,230 --> 00:12:49,940
Centuries of my clan's work,
all ruined by that brat!

156
00:12:53,590 --> 00:13:00,200
Once I complete my great plan,
I'll flay him alive and tear out his tendons!

157
00:13:01,990 --> 00:13:06,780
Sect Master, we've searched
the surrounding area, but there's no sign of Sima Jiao.

158
00:13:08,110 --> 00:13:10,250
He was already gravely injured.

159
00:13:10,250 --> 00:13:13,400
In such a short time, how could he just vanish?

160
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:15,410
Keep searching!

161
00:13:15,410 --> 00:13:18,400
Bring him back to me,
even if you have to dig deep into the ground!

162
00:13:18,400 --> 00:13:19,940
Understood.

163
00:13:27,340 --> 00:13:31,000
Father, what should we do next?

164
00:13:31,800 --> 00:13:34,960
Sima Jiao was badly wounded in the siege.

165
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:40,320
With his condition, even if he hides for a few days,
it won't help him.

166
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:44,960
Now that my plan is exposed and Baifeng Mountain is destroyed,

167
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:51,300
our only option
is to take advantage of his injuries and seal him away again.

168
00:13:51,300 --> 00:13:55,030
But with Baifeng Mountain exposed, I fear the Eight Palaces may...

169
00:13:55,030 --> 00:13:59,440
They are too busy hunting Sima Jiao right now to think about that!

170
00:13:59,990 --> 00:14:02,920
Zhen Xu, clean this place up.

171
00:14:02,920 --> 00:14:06,400
Don't leave a single witness alive.

172
00:14:06,400 --> 00:14:07,840
Yes, Father.

173
00:14:26,940 --> 00:14:29,560
You're a demonic cultivator, aren't you?

174
00:14:32,820 --> 00:14:34,890
Me, a demonic cultivator?

175
00:14:34,890 --> 00:14:38,030
 If the Sect Master or the other palace heads learn your true identity, 

176
00:14:38,030 --> 00:14:40,680
 do you think Sima Jiao will still protect you? 

177
00:14:40,680 --> 00:14:46,150
Well, even though I'm a demonic cultivator, I don't think I've ever harmed anyone.

178
00:14:47,320 --> 00:14:49,230
Don't be nervous, Miss.

179
00:14:49,230 --> 00:14:51,050
I know.

180
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:58,600
My eyes can tell good from evil, so I know you are not one of the wicked.

181
00:14:59,280 --> 00:15:00,630
Thank goodness.

182
00:15:00,630 --> 00:15:01,920
You scared me.

183
00:15:01,920 --> 00:15:04,860
I thought you were going to take my life.

184
00:15:04,860 --> 00:15:09,160
Many years ago, I met Sima Jiao once at Three Saints Mountain.

185
00:15:09,160 --> 00:15:11,200
He was still very young then,

186
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:15,870
yet he already showed extraordinary intelligence and insight.

187
00:15:15,870 --> 00:15:18,920
I gave him the Taoist name "Mercy"

188
00:15:18,920 --> 00:15:22,200
in hopes that he would
have compassion for living beings

189
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:24,990
and restrain his urge to kill.

190
00:15:24,990 --> 00:15:27,860
I foresaw

191
00:15:27,860 --> 00:15:32,010
that he would single-handedly
destroy Gengchen Celestial Palace,

192
00:15:32,010 --> 00:15:37,710
nearly overturn the entire cultivation world, and slaughter countless innocent mortals.

193
00:15:42,680 --> 00:15:45,350
Fertile lands would be scorched barren.

194
00:15:45,350 --> 00:15:48,470
The Immortal Realm would become hell.

195
00:15:48,470 --> 00:15:50,630
The world would fall into devastation.

196
00:15:50,630 --> 00:15:53,260
And he would commit terrible sins.

197
00:15:55,080 --> 00:15:59,970
The Grandmaster may look ruthless, but he doesn't kill indiscriminately.

198
00:16:06,040 --> 00:16:08,590
Nothing in this world is absolute.

199
00:16:08,590 --> 00:16:12,040
Even in a dead end,
there may be a thread of hope.

200
00:16:12,040 --> 00:16:17,640
In his blood-soaked, murderous future, I caught sight of a faint glimmer of life.

201
00:16:17,640 --> 00:16:22,070
So, I foretold that he would one day
encounter a turning point,

202
00:16:22,070 --> 00:16:25,130
a person who would change him.

203
00:16:25,130 --> 00:16:27,290
Who is that person?

204
00:16:30,750 --> 00:16:33,980
Back then, I left a prayer bead on him

205
00:16:33,980 --> 00:16:37,930
to suppress his viciousness and help keep his mind clear.

206
00:16:37,930 --> 00:16:41,180
But at the same time,
if he gave in to killing intent,

207
00:16:41,180 --> 00:16:43,930
he would be overcome by unbearable pain.

208
00:16:50,940 --> 00:16:54,470
So, this bead isn't just an ornament.

209
00:16:54,470 --> 00:16:59,940
This prayer bead is seen by others
only as a seal that binds him.

210
00:16:59,940 --> 00:17:03,130
From the day it was put on,
no one has been able to remove it.

211
00:17:03,130 --> 00:17:07,210
But in truth, it is also a divine medicine.

212
00:17:07,210 --> 00:17:11,410
If you can undo this seal, the bead can save his life once.

213
00:17:11,410 --> 00:17:17,080
If not, it means Sima Jiao never found that spark of hope,

214
00:17:17,080 --> 00:17:21,300
and today will be his end.

215
00:17:21,300 --> 00:17:24,000
Can't you just save him yourself?

216
00:17:26,820 --> 00:17:29,310
Why don't you try?

217
00:18:08,820 --> 00:18:10,470
I thought so.

218
00:18:10,470 --> 00:18:13,200
Since you are Sima Jiao's one chance at life,

219
00:18:13,200 --> 00:18:16,110
you are also the hope of all living beings.

220
00:18:16,920 --> 00:18:20,840
I ask that you guide Sima Jiao from now on.

221
00:18:20,840 --> 00:18:22,960
Lead him toward the good.

222
00:18:24,640 --> 00:18:27,360
There are other Spirit Fires in the world.

223
00:18:27,360 --> 00:18:32,250
Tell him to handle them with care and use them for righteous deeds.

224
00:18:32,250 --> 00:18:34,960
Other Spirit Fires?

225
00:18:34,960 --> 00:18:37,510
What do you mean?

226
00:18:37,510 --> 00:18:39,640
Pass the message to Sima Jiao.

227
00:18:39,640 --> 00:18:41,970
He will understand.

228
00:18:43,510 --> 00:18:44,920
But look at him now.

229
00:18:44,920 --> 00:18:47,360
He's gravely injured.

230
00:18:47,360 --> 00:18:50,260
No number of bandages would be enough.

231
00:18:50,260 --> 00:18:51,960
Master...

232
00:18:53,450 --> 00:18:54,610
Master?

233
00:18:54,610 --> 00:18:58,200
My connection with the Fengshan Clan ends here.

234
00:18:58,200 --> 00:19:00,710
Take care.

235
00:19:00,710 --> 00:19:03,150
You're leaving just like that?

236
00:19:10,920 --> 00:19:15,680
This bead was taken off your ankle,

237
00:19:16,360 --> 00:19:19,350
but surely you wouldn't mind, right?

238
00:19:30,360 --> 00:19:33,340
 His complexion looks better than before. 

239
00:19:43,960 --> 00:19:46,720
Finally, I've managed to save you for once.

240
00:19:48,620 --> 00:19:52,340
 ♫ Mountains and rivers shatter before my eyes ♫ 

241
00:19:52,340 --> 00:19:55,540
 ♫ Endless splendor
cultivated through lifetimes ♫ 

242
00:19:55,540 --> 00:20:00,300
 ♫ Turns to dust between my fingers
in an instant ♫ 

243
00:20:00,300 --> 00:20:03,900
 ♫ When the line
between good and evil is clear ♫ 

244
00:20:03,900 --> 00:20:08,340
 ♫ Countless souls drift
into the boundless wilds ♫ 

245
00:20:10,230 --> 00:20:13,270
You have the face of a delicate, pretty boy,

246
00:20:13,270 --> 00:20:17,110
yet you endured it all without ever once crying out in pain.

247
00:20:17,110 --> 00:20:21,980
 ♫ Falling into love's abyss like heavy rain ♫ 

248
00:20:21,980 --> 00:20:24,680
 ♫ Pouring down ♫ 

249
00:20:24,680 --> 00:20:28,500
 ♫ Drunk on romance ♫ 

250
00:20:28,500 --> 00:20:32,100
 ♫ In a blink, love and hate
vanish into illusion ♫ 

251
00:20:32,100 --> 00:20:37,420
 ♫ Falling into endless love, stirring waves ♫ 

252
00:20:37,420 --> 00:20:40,600
 ♫ Upending a lifetime ♫ 

253
00:20:40,600 --> 00:20:42,890
Sima Jiao.

254
00:20:42,890 --> 00:20:45,410
Please wake up.

255
