and attain immortality.

313
00:24:39,260 --> 00:24:40,860
Yes.

314
00:24:40,860 --> 00:24:46,980
When we achieve our goal, I will kill Sima Jiao to avenge An Xue!

315
00:24:55,840 --> 00:24:57,400
